name: Bolivar Rotation
description: The heroes of all latitudes are taught as superhuman beings who fought for the freedoms of all and must be revered, they overlook the fact that they were ordinary human beings, who perhaps were fighting for their own interests rather than for the freedom of their countrymen, even attacking their own people, We must not deny their invaluable contributions that we like to not build our societies, but we must keep them present in all their nuances no matter how dark they may be.
